h6 15. Rf3 $18) 15. Qh3 $36 c5 {Most of White's pieces are contributing in a
way to White's attack, the exception being one major piece. Hence this is the
right moment to bring it into the game!} 16. Rcd1 $1 {[%cal Gd1d8]}) 14. Bc2 $1
