{1/2-1/2 (38) Harika,D (2495)-L'Ami,E (2622) Vlissingen NED 2019}) 16... Nxg4
17. Qxg4 Bf6 18. Qh3 h6 19. g4 $36 {[%cal Gg4g5]}) 14. Nxf6+ Bxf6 15. dxc5 {
