20. Rcd1 $1 {Yet again! White keeps the initiative.}) 17. Rcd1 (17. f5 {
This move weakens the e5-square, so Black captures on d4} cxd4 18. exd4 Bxd4+
19. Kh1 Qh4 20. Nxd5 Ne5 $1 21. Qe4 Qxe4 22. Bxe4 Bxd5 23. Bxd5 Rad8 $132 24.
