bishop, is achieved easily.}) 10. Qb1 {Transposes to the main line.}) (8... c5
9. a3 {Of course!} Bxc3 10. Bxc3 c4 (10... Ne4 11. dxc5 (11. h4 h6 12. Ne5 Nxc3
