exf7+ Kxf7 19. Be2 {1/2-1/2 (131) Alpha Zero-Stockfish 8 London ENG 2018}) (
10... c5 11. dxc5 bxc5 12. e4 $14) 11. b4 a6 (11... Ne4 12. Nb5 Bf8 13. Rc1 Na6
{Now this knight is misplaced on a6.} 14. a3 c5 15. bxc5 bxc5 16. Be1 $1 {
