Naxc5 $11 {1-0 (76) Stern, R (2513)-Dragun,K (2547) Bochum GER 2014}) {After}
16... c4 {White has} 17. Nc3 $1 $14 {[%csl Ra6][%cal Gb1b7]}) 12. b5 (12. Rc1
Nbd7 13. a4 Ne4 $1 $132 (13... Nf8 $6 14. b5 a5 15. Rc2 $1 Ne4 16. Bc1 {
