White won comforably in 1-0 (44) Sandipan,C (2545) -Vaibhav,S (2597) Majitar
IND 2019 The Week in Chess 1311})) 12... axb5 (12... a5 13. Qb3 $1 Ne4 (13...
Nbd7 14. Bc1 {[%cal Gc1a3]}) 14. Rad1 {[%csl Rd5] Black cannot play Nbd7 as
