Rd5 46. Rh1 f1=Q {1-0 (46) Ivanisevic, I (2574)-Pavlovic, M (2482) Valjevo SRB
2018}) 8. Ne2 d6 (8... Qh4 9. g3 Qf6 10. f4 Nxc3 11. Nxc3 cxd4 12. Qxd4 Qxd4
