bxc4 Qc7 15. Nd2 {Not only removing the knight from the a8-h1 diagonal but
also stopping Black from playing Nh5.} (15. Qe2 Nh5 $1 $132 {1/2-1/2 (32)
Sandipan, C (2579)-Nihal,S (2524) Caleta ENG 2018}) 15... Qc6 (15... Rfd8 16.
Rc1 $14 {[%csl Gc1][%cal Gc1c8]}) 16. f3 e5 17. d5 Qc5+ 18. Kh1 {, with a
pleasant position. if} b5 19. cxb5 Nxd5 20. Qb1 $14 *

